---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Submit a Theme"
    description="Submit your theme idea for the Bermuda Triangle Society book club. Help us pick what we'll read next!"
>
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <section
        class="bg-linear-to-b from-mystic-900 to-mystic-800 text-white py-16 md:py-20"
    >
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <span
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-lantern-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide mb-4"
            >
                <i class="fa-solid fa-sharp fa-lightbulb"></i>
                Get Involved
            </span>
            <h1
                class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-6"
            >
                Submit a Theme
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-mystic-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Have an idea for our next reading theme? We'd love to hear it!
                The best themes spark curiosity and let readers explore in
                different directions.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <section class="py-16 md:py-20 transition-colors duration-300">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
            <!-- What Makes a Good Theme -->
            <div class="mb-12">
                <h2
                    class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-mystic-900 dark:text-mystic-100 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3"
                >
                    <span class="text-lantern-500"
                        ><i class="fa-solid fa-sharp fa-sparkles"></i></span
                    >
                    What Makes a Good Theme?
                </h2>

                <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
                    <div class="card p-5 border-l-4 border-l-bermuda-500">
                        <h3
                            class="font-semibold text-mystic-800 dark:text-mystic-200 mb-2"
                        >
                            Broad Enough
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-mystic-600 dark:text-mystic-400">
                            Multiple books should fit, across different
                            subgenres and styles.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card p-5 border-l-4 border-l-bermuda-500">
                        <h3
                            class="font-semibold text-mystic-800 dark:text-mystic-200 mb-2"
                        >
                            Specific Enough
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-mystic-600 dark:text-mystic-400">
                            Not so vague that "everything counts." Give us
                            something to explore.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card p-5 border-l-4 border-l-lantern-500">
                        <h3
                            class="font-semibold text-mystic-800 dark:text-mystic-200 mb-2"
                        >
                            Spark Curiosity
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-mystic-600 dark:text-mystic-400">
                            The best themes make people think "Oh, I know a book
                            for that!"
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card p-5 border-l-4 border-l-lantern-500">
                        <h3
                            class="font-semibold text-mystic-800 dark:text-mystic-200 mb-2"
                        >
                            Accessible
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-mystic-600 dark:text-mystic-400">
                            Books should be findable at libraries, on Libby, or
                            at reasonable prices.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Example Themes -->
            <div class="mb-12">
                <h2
                    class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-mystic-900 dark:text-mystic-100 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3"
                >
                    <span class="text-mystic-500"
                        ><i class="fa-solid fa-sharp fa-books"></i></span
                    >
                    Example Themes
                </h2>

                <div class="grid gap-3">
                    <div
                        class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-mystic-950 rounded-xl border border-mystic-100 dark:border-mystic-800"
                    >
                        <span class="text-xl text-bermuda-500"
                            ><i class="fa-solid fa-sharp fa-water"></i></span
                        >
                        <div>
                            <span
                                class="font-semibold text-mystic-800 dark:text-mystic-200"
                                >Lost at Sea</span
                            >
                            <span
                                class="text-mystic-500 dark:text-mystic-400 text-sm ml-2"
                                >— Shipwrecks, ocean mysteries, underwater
                                worlds</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-mystic-950 rounded-xl border border-mystic-100 dark:border-mystic-800"
                    >
                        <span class="text-xl text-lantern-500"
                            ><i class="fa-solid fa-sharp fa-rotate"></i></span
                        >
                        <div>
                            <span
                                class="font-semibold text-mystic-800 dark:text-mystic-200"
                                >Time Loops & Reset Stories</span
                            >
                            <span
                                class="text-mystic-500 dark:text-mystic-400 text-sm ml-2"
                                >— Groundhog Day energy, but with lasers or
                                murder</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-mystic-950 rounded-xl border border-mystic-100 dark:border-mystic-800"
                    >
                        <span class="text-xl text-mystic-500"
                            ><i class="fa-solid fa-sharp fa-people-group"
                            ></i></span
                        >
                        <div>
                            <span
                                class="font-semibold text-mystic-800 dark:text-mystic-200"
                                >Found Family (But Make It Weird)</span
                            >
                            <span
                                class="text-mystic-500 dark:text-mystic-400 text-sm ml-2"
                                >— Chosen families in strange circumstances</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-mystic-950 rounded-xl border border-mystic-100 dark:border-mystic-800"
                    >
                        <span class="text-xl text-mystic-500"
                            ><i class="fa-solid fa-sharp fa-masks-theater"
                            ></i></span
                        >
                        <div>
                            <span
                                class="font-semibold text-mystic-800 dark:text-mystic-200"
                                >Unreliable Narrators</span
                            >
                            <span
                                class="text-mystic-500 dark:text-mystic-400 text-sm ml-2"
                                >— When you can't trust who's telling the story</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-mystic-950 rounded-xl border border-mystic-100 dark:border-mystic-800"
                    >
                        <span class="text-xl text-lantern-500"
                            ><i class="fa-solid fa-sharp fa-mug-hot"></i></span
                        >
                        <div>
                            <span
                                class="font-semibold text-mystic-800 dark:text-mystic-200"
                                >Cozy Apocalypse</span
                            >
                            <span
                                class="text-mystic-500 dark:text-mystic-400 text-sm ml-2"
                                >— The world ends, but there's still tea</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Submission Form Placeholder -->
            <div
                class="card p-8 bg-linear-to-br from-mystic-100 to-mystic-300 dark:to-mystic-600"
            >
                <h2
                    class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-mystic-950 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"
                >
                    <span class="text-bermuda-500"
                        ><i class="fa-solid fa-sharp fa-pen-to-square"
                        ></i></span
                    >
                    Submit Your Idea
                </h2>

                <iframe
                    data-tally-src="https://tally.so/embed/obM1O5?alignLeft=1&hideTitle=1&transparentBackground=1"
                    loading="lazy"
                    width="100%"
                    height="484"
                    frameborder="0"
                    marginheight="0"
                    marginwidth="0"
                    title="Bermuda Triangle Society Themes"></iframe>
                <script>
                    var d = document,
                        w = "https://tally.so/widgets/embed.js",
                        v = function () {
                            "undefined" != typeof Tally
                                ? Tally.loadEmbeds()
                                : d
                                      .querySelectorAll(
                                          "iframe[data-tally-src]:not([src])",
                                      )
                                      .forEach(function (e) {
                                          e.src = e.dataset.tallySrc;
                                      });
                        };
                    if ("undefined" != typeof Tally) v();
                    else if (
                        d.querySelector('script[src="' + w + '"]') == null
                    ) {
                        var s = d.createElement("script");
                        ((s.src = w),
                            (s.onload = v),
                            (s.onerror = v),
                            d.body.appendChild(s));
                    }
                </script>
            </div>

            <!-- Alternative Contact -->
            <div class="mt-8 text-center">
                <p class="text-mystic-600 dark:text-mystic-400 mb-4">
                    Want to share your idea another way?
                </p>
                <a
                    href="/meetings"
                    class="text-mystic-700 dark:text-mystic-300 hover:text-mystic-900 dark:hover:text-mystic-100 font-medium"
                >
                    Bring it to our next meeting <i
                        class="fa-solid fa-sharp fa-arrow-right"></i>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section
        class="py-12 bg-mystic-100 dark:bg-mystic-900 transition-colors duration-300"
    >
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
            <h2
                class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-mystic-900 dark:text-mystic-100 mb-6 text-center"
            >
                Theme Questions
            </h2>

            <div class="space-y-4">
                <details class="card p-4 group">
                    <summary
                        class="font-semibold text-mystic-800 dark:text-mystic-200 cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between"
                    >
                        Can I submit multiple themes?
                        <i
                            class="fa-solid fa-sharp fa-chevron-down text-mystic-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"
                        ></i>
                    </summary>
                    <p
                        class="mt-3 text-mystic-600 dark:text-mystic-400 text-sm"
                    >
                        Absolutely! Submit as many as you like. We'll add them
                        all to the pool for future votes.
                    </p>
                </details>

                <details class="card p-4 group">
                    <summary
                        class="font-semibold text-mystic-800 dark:text-mystic-200 cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between"
                    >
                        How are themes chosen?
                        <i
                            class="fa-solid fa-sharp fa-chevron-down text-mystic-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"
                        ></i>
                    </summary>
                    <p
                        class="mt-3 text-mystic-600 dark:text-mystic-400 text-sm"
                    >
                        At each meeting, we vote from the theme pool. The
                        winning theme becomes next month's focus. Popular themes
                        that don't win stay in the pool for future votes.
                    </p>
                </details>

                <details class="card p-4 group">
                    <summary
                        class="font-semibold text-mystic-800 dark:text-mystic-200 cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between"
                    >
                        Can themes be specific to a subgenre?
                        <i
                            class="fa-solid fa-sharp fa-chevron-down text-mystic-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"
                        ></i>
                    </summary>
                    <p
                        class="mt-3 text-mystic-600 dark:text-mystic-400 text-sm"
                    >
                        Yes! Themes like "Space Opera" or "Urban Fantasy" are
                        great. Just make sure there are enough accessible books
                        that fit.
                    </p>
                </details>

                <details class="card p-4 group">
                    <summary
                        class="font-semibold text-mystic-800 dark:text-mystic-200 cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between"
                    >
                        What if my theme was already done?
                        <i
                            class="fa-solid fa-sharp fa-chevron-down text-mystic-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"
                        ></i>
                    </summary>
                    <p
                        class="mt-3 text-mystic-600 dark:text-mystic-400 text-sm"
                    >
                        Popular themes can always come back! If enough time has
                        passed and there's interest, we might revisit a
                        theme—there are always more books to discover.
                    </p>
                </details>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
